HEADWORD: Hematein
<hw>Hem`a*te"in</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/, <?/,
blood.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>A reddish brown or violet
